{
  "stem": "12255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what he used to do was to pack as many people as he could into the van, take a lot of prayer books along as well, and he would drive through into France.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He already had the-- many of the border guards were already sort of being smoothed over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as he spoke French and one thing and another, if he was stopped by somebody who didn't know, he was going to a service.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was-- look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's a Magen David, and there's all this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so he carried on this activity for many, many months, ferrying people out of Germany down to Marseille.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and there, they waited their turn to try and get onto the small boats and so on that were, were carrying out this duty.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, but I knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That Rosh Hashanah, the second Rosh-- my second Rosh Hashanah, 1946 now-- I had-- by that time, the Jewish soldiers, thousands had been demobbed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my congregation had shrunk very, very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was able to hold my High Holy Day services in the Jewish club in Brunswick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was no longer stationed in Iserlohn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd be moved to Luneberg, well known place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now-- another half hour?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and on Yom Kippur in afternoon, the club was closed of course, and we were holding services.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Abraham was assisting me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a banging on the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody went, and they came up and said, the military police would like to see me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took off my tallit, and I went down to see what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said they want to see Abraham Goldfinger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and they wanted to interview him and see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
